[32mв”Ӯ[0m ### thoughts                                                                                                                                                                          [32mв”Ӯ[0m
[32mв”Ӯ[0m                                                                                                                                                                                       [32mв”Ӯ[0m
[32mв”Ӯ[0m **Why this payload worked:** The application uses Ruby ERB (Embedded Ruby) templating engine to render user input. The `sentence` parameter is directly interpolated into an ERB      [32mв”Ӯ[0m
[32mв”Ӯ[0m template without sanitization. Ruby ERB evaluates `<%= ruby_code %>` expressions and backticks (`) execute system commands in Ruby.                                                   [32mв”Ӯ[0m
[32mв”Ӯ[0m                                                                                                                                                                                       [32mв”Ӯ[0m
[32mв”Ӯ[0m **Input validation bypass:** The server initially rejected raw `<%=7*7%>` with "invalid %-encoding" error, suggesting basic input filtering. URL-encoding the payload                 [32mв”Ӯ[0m
[32mв”Ӯ[0m (`%3C%25%3D7%2A7%25%3E`) bypassed this filter, and the application decoded it before passing to the ERB renderer.                                                                     [32mв”Ӯ[0m
[32mв”Ӯ[0m                                                                                                                                                                                       [32mв”Ӯ[0m
[32mв”Ӯ[0m **Security implications:**                                                                                                                                                            [32mв”Ӯ[0m
[32mв”Ӯ[0m - Remote code execution as root (uid=0)                                                                                                                                               [32mв”Ӯ[0m
[32mв”Ӯ[0m - Full system access including all files and directories                                                                                                                              [32mв”Ӯ[0m
[32mв”Ӯ[0m - Potential for lateral movement, persistence, and complete system compromise                                                                                                         [32mв”Ӯ[0m
[32mв”Ӯ[0m                                                                                                                                                                                       [32mв”Ӯ[0m
[32mв”Ӯ[0m **Next steps (for remediation):**                                                                                                                                                     [32mв”Ӯ[0m
[32mв”Ӯ[0m - Never pass user input directly to template engines                                                                                                                                  [32mв”Ӯ[0m
[32mв”Ӯ[0m - Use parameterized templates with allowlisted variables                                                                                                                              [32mв”Ӯ[0m
[32mв”Ӯ[0m - Implement input validation and output encoding                                                                                                                                      [32mв”Ӯ[0m
[32mв”Ӯ[0m - Run applications with minimal privileges (not as root)                                                                                                                              [32mв”Ӯ[0m
