[35mв”Ӯ[0m thoughts:                                                                                                                                                                             [35mв”Ӯ[0m
[35mв”Ӯ[0m **Why this payload worked:** The application uses Ruby ERB (Embedded Ruby) templating engine to render user input. The `sentence` parameter is directly interpolated into an ERB      [35mв”Ӯ[0m
[35mв”Ӯ[0m template without sanitization. Ruby ERB evaluates `<%= ruby_code %>` expressions, and backticks (`) execute system commands in Ruby.                                                  [35mв”Ӯ[0m
[35mв”Ӯ[0m                                                                                                                                                                                       [35mв”Ӯ[0m
[35mв”Ӯ[0m **Input validation bypass:** The server initially rejected raw `<%=7*7%>` with "invalid %-encoding" error, indicating basic input filtering. URL-encoding the payload                 [35mв”Ӯ[0m
[35mв”Ӯ[0m (`%3C%25%3D7%2A7%25%3E`) bypassed this filter, and the application decoded it before passing to the ERB renderer.                                                                     [35mв”Ӯ[0m
[35mв”Ӯ[0m                                                                                                                                                                                       [35mв”Ӯ[0m
[35mв”Ӯ[0m **Security implications:**                                                                                                                                                            [35mв”Ӯ[0m
[35mв”Ӯ[0m - Remote code execution as root (uid=0)                                                                                                                                               [35mв”Ӯ[0m
[35mв”Ӯ[0m - Full system access including all files and directories                                                                                                                              [35mв”Ӯ[0m
[35mв”Ӯ[0m - Complete system compromise possible                                                                                                                                                 [35mв”Ӯ[0m
[35mв”Ӯ[0m                                                                                                                                                                                       [35mв”Ӯ[0m
[35mв”Ӯ[0m **Remediation recommendations:**                                                                                                                                                      [35mв”Ӯ[0m
[35mв”Ӯ[0m - Never pass user input directly to template engines                                                                                                                                  [35mв”Ӯ[0m
[35mв”Ӯ[0m - Use parameterized templates with allowlisted variables                                                                                                                              [35mв”Ӯ[0m
[35mв”Ӯ[0m - Implement strict input validation and output encoding                                                                                                                               [35mв”Ӯ[0m
[35mв”Ӯ[0m - Run applications with minimal privileges (not as root)                                                                                                                              [35mв”Ӯ[0m
[35mв”Ӯ[0m - Consider template engine sandboxing or alternative rendering approaches                                                                                                             [35mв”Ӯ[0m
[35mв”Ӯ[0m                                                                                                                                                                                       [35mв”Ӯ[0m
